Title: Awesome Portugal
DateModified: '2019-02-28'
DatePublished: '2019-02-28'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/awesome-portugal
SetInCountry: Portugal
Category: I didn't expect to find
AuthorName: Dimphina Pereira
AuthorCountry: India
Text: I have travelled to Jakarta Indonesia.I have travelled to botg the islands Java
  and Sumatra.I have also been to Bali.Bali is a beautiful place .I have been to Singapore,.I
  enjoyed the food and the culture in Singapore.I love the smells of Singapore.I have
  been to Batam too.Then I travelled to Kuala Lumpur Malaysia .I have enjoyed the
  culture and the food there too.Then I travelled to Istanbul.Istanbul is lovely.Then
  to Albania.I love Albania especially the beaches Duress,Vlore,Sarande are extremely
  beautiful.Then I travelled to Athens Greece.Greece too is Beautiful .From Greece
  I travelled to Doha Qatar.Enjoyed my trip in Doha Qatar.My last trip was Bangkok
  Thailand.I enjoyed the food,shopping and culture in Thailand.I even made new Thai
  friends .It was fun trip.I really enjoyed my travel.Now I am looking forward to
  travel to Portugal a place  where I haven't been and only heard off.I would love
  to go to Portugal the land of my ancestors.I would like to explore the unknown and
  gain experience.Awaiting the trip to Portugal soon.
